       true,
       "abc.get_cache_token.__name__.__eq__('get_cache_token') == True — get_cache_token returns an integer token that changes each time an ABC is registered; its __name__ is 'get_cache_token' (15 chars: g-e-t-_-c-a-c-h-e-_-t-o-k-e-n); str.__eq__('get_cache_token') returns True; new to extra176"]
