       true,
       "abc.get_cache_token.__module__.__eq__('_abc') == True — get_cache_token is implemented in the C extension module _abc for performance; the abc module re-exports it; its __module__ is '_abc' (not 'abc'); str.__eq__('_abc') returns True; new to extra176"]
    - [gct_qualname_eq,
