       "abc.get_cache_token.__qualname__.__eq__('get_cache_token') == True — get_cache_token is a module-level function so its __qualname__ equals its __name__; str.__eq__('get_cache_token') returns True; new to extra176"]
    - [gct_class_name_eq,
